      "value": "<p><a href=\"https://aonprd.com/RacesDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Samsaran\">Samsaran</a>&nbsp;only.</p>\n<p>Samsaran slayers are adept at obscuring the passes of their mountain homes from intruders. The slayer can cast @Compendium[pf1.spells.kq916lznxo0ig68v]{Silent Image}&nbsp;as a spell-like ability once per day for every 2 slayer levels he has, using his slayer level as his caster level. The slayer uses his Intelligence modifier on concentration checks when using this ability, and the DC to disbelieve the illusion is equal to 11 + the slayerâ€™s Intelligence modifier.</p>\n<p>The slayer must have an Intelligence score of at least 11 to select this talent.</p>",
